Note: Date based on dates of 1st World War. "Visa, No. 14.804." appears on the bottom right of poster. Orientation: Vertical.
Description: Text in French says that there will be a victory exposition to profit the National Committee of Physical and Sport Education and Social Hygiene. It will be March 11th to and including April 1st. Illustration shows an angel with wings susspended in air, symbolic of victory.
